<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.3">
<l>kāṇkiṉṟa nilamellām yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kāṇkiṉṟa vicumpellām yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kāṇkiṉṟa ventīyellām yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kāṇkiṉṟa vikkāṟṟellām yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kāṇkiṉṟa kaṭalellām yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kāṇkiṉṟa kaṭalvaṇṇa ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>kāṇkiṉṟa vulakat tīrkkeṉ collukēṉ kāṇkiṉṟa veṉkā rikaicey kiṉṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I [am] all the ground that is seen”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I am all the sky that is seen”, she says,</l>
<l>“I [am] all the hot fire that is seen”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I [am] all the wind that is seen”, she says,</l>
<l>“I [am] all the ocean that is seen”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the one of ocean colour that is seen settles in [her]?</l>
<l>What will I say to you of the world that is seen,</l>
	[words also] made by my girl that is seen?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
